					<text transform="translate(182.58 2319.24)" font-size="29" fill="#004278" font-family="shippori-mincho,sans-serif" font-weight="500" style="isolation: isolate;">中川　真</text>
					<text transform="translate(173.8 2345.16)" font-size="19" fill="#00457e" font-family="sawarabi-mincho,sans-serif" font-weight="500" style="isolation: isolate;">(平成27年入社)</text>
