					<text transform="translate(37.31 2157.74)" font-size="24.63" fill="#fff" font-family="sawarabi-mincho,sans-serif" font-weight="500" style="isolation: isolate;">スキルアップには最適だと思います</text>
					<text transform="translate(431.38 2157.74)" font-size="24.63" fill="#fff" font-family="sawarabi-mincho,sans-serif" font-weight="500" letter-spacing="-0.5em" style="isolation: isolate;">。</text>
